flowchart LR
    A[Usuario] -->|email + senha| B[NextAuth]
    B -->|POST /auth/login| C[FastAPI]
    C -->|valida bcrypt| D[(PostgreSQL)]
    D --> C
    C -->|access + refresh token| B
    B -->|session JWT| A

    E[Token expirando] -->|POST /auth/refresh| C
    C -->|novo token| E

    F[Logout] -->|blacklist token| G[(Redis)]
